y\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27047,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/01\/20\/most-haya-uthman\/","url_meta":{"origin":36955,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Uthman: Most modest of the Ummah is Uthman","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 20, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cModesty is part of faith, and the most modest of my nation is Uthman.\u201d Source: Ta\u0304ri\u0304kh Dimashq li-Ibn 'Asa\u0304kir 39\/92 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35715,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/20\/uthman-bored-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":36955,"position":2},"title":"Uthman on Quran: If we were pure, never bored of Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 20, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Sufyan reported: Uthman, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cIf our hearts were pure, we would never be tired of the speech of Allah.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304\u2019 7\/272 \u0639\u0646 \u0633\u064f\u0641\u0652\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0646 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u064