lias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/05\/15\/best-ummah-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":36955,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Caliphs: Best of Ummah are Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 15, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: In the lifetime of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, while his companions were numerous, we preferred Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman, then we would remain silent. Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 4626 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut Imam Ahmad commented, \u201cThe best of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14284,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/19\/wudu-salat-expiate-sins\/","url_meta":{"origin":36955,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Salah: Excellent ablution, prayer erases minor sins","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 19, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Uthman ibn Affan reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"No Muslim attends a prescribed prayer and performs its ablution, reverence, and bowing in the best manner, but that it will be an expiation for his previous sins as long as he did not commit\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/36955","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v